Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後去邀請一下螢 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5點集合喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 聽到了嗎 揶子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉抱歉 在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那5點見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能先去聯絡一下螢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 只要等一等他們都會來的…我是…這樣想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 我現在跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 她在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你在幹什麽啊螢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買一根 這種冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全壘打棒 不說都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個棒狀的雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是日本最初以棒狀冰淇淋改良而成的産品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是日本第一個帶中獎的冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻著全壘打和安打的棒子混在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了已經深入人心的 中了奬就可以再來一根的規則以外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還可以獲得各種各樣的奬品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你想中全壘打捧 才那麼認真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…我一直都很認真的選啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛也確實是特别認真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什麽意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能中就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在開店的角度來説不是不中更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是免費送一根哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算螢沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為從廠商進貨時中奬數量就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換奬時店裡也不會有損失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是呢 不愧是開店的九
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不快出門的話就要趕不上公交了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原來你有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊有煙花晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天想是要邀請螢一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一趟公交是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩小時後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 九
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子沒接？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該沒啥事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這麽大的人流量 碰頭估計有點困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在趕過來沒注意到有電話也説不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有辦法見到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能有點别的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…話説我也不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去和沙耶和豆碰頭 4個人一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才説要邀請螢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自已覺得有點安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有時間説出自己想説的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個其實今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 讓你煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天想要兩個人聊一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了九
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了應有的樣子和態度是什麽樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從咖啡遠藤的兩人那也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麽快樂的暑假還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始到這裡的目的 現在好像也沒什麽關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就想和你聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡能看到海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後得向他們兩個道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全壘打棒 中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢中奬了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽什麽都抽不中的螢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前沒説過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是相當健忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不會丟了 你幫我拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次突然想吃全壘打棒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能吃到免費的 會覺得賺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為要親上來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 能代我向他們兩人道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,説對不起獨估了九
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天下雨了 所以要説理由 應該是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭淋雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天也下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 理由很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來躲雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你拿毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後一直是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰的嗎還是熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 最近沒看到螢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天來了
